<h2>Teaching Languages on the Screen: Translating Cultures, Images and Words/ Insegnare le lingue al cinema: tradurre culture, immagini e parole (Veranstaltungsprojekt)</h2>
<h3>Grundtvig-Fortbildungskurs - Siena, 3.-7. September 2012 - Deadline: 26.04.2012</h3>
<hr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
